Body:
What We've Learned Updated: our Korean partner 'CoSoSys Korea' reported am issue where EasyLock opens without a password.
This issue occurs with the EPP installation image ("epp5810-64-mainline.iso" ISO Image) that we supplied to our Korean Partner for distribution to Korean end customers.
Next Steps Updated: Request was made to our R&D team to build a new ISO install image which will contain the fix.
